Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:19.39,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Dii! Prišiel si pre mňa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:25.67,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže sa zobudil z vlastnej vôle...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:53.17,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I let my childhood dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:56.37,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Flow freely out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:01:00.17,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,In scribbles that don't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:05.75,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,And they connect to the future I conceive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.45,0:01:11.34,Utawarerumono2,,0000,0000,0000,,Utawarerumono
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:17.29,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,The clear sky, endlessly blue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.23,0:01:24.50,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Captivates me, my heart is filled with innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:28.77,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll soon gain wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:31.71,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,That will let me fly freely about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:36.41,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,My innocent eyes go on searching
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:40.05,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go beyond the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:43.38,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all my endless wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:46.69,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,If only one of them comes true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:50.32,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to give it up to anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:54.33,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to grasp my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:57.67,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,My childhood dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:02:01.00,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever continued to be drawn out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:04.67,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,In scribbles that don't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:10.01,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,They connect to a future I wish for
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.96,0:02:24.73,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže sa ubránili použitím nejakej obrovskej sily?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:26.93,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0160,,Tam kde leží srdce
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:28.43,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, kým sme prišli,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:32.76,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Hauenkuaujin tým Avu Kamu bol úplne zničený.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:36.16,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš mi tým povedať, že existuje\N niečo, čo je silnejšie ako Avu Kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:38.60,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:41.67,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si to urobil?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:44.15,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím o prepáčenie, Vaša Výsosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:48.17,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak budeme pokračovať takto, čaká nás len cesta záhuby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:52.15,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vaša Výsosť, zjedotenie je už skoro na dosah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.14,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz nemôžeme ustúpiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:58.65,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vaša Výsosť, naozaj teraz chcete\N zmeniť svoje rozhodnutie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:01.73,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Hien, váž svoje slová.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.42,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,V poriadku, Genjimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:06.03,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Sľúbila som
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:08.44,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,poskytnúť bezpečný život ľuďom Kunekamanu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:11.41,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže chcete poštvať všetky\N národy proti nám kvôli tomuto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:16.30,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Už je pre nás príliž neskoro ustúpiť z vojny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.03,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo chcete odo mňa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.49,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vycítili ste moju prítomnosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.20,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Správne. Kto ste?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:45.37,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo máte spoločné s Hauenkuou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:49.71,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Som sám. Nikdo viac nie je.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:52.38,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemám záujem o hádanky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:53.85,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak mi neodpoviete...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:58.09,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Zostarol si, Genjimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:02.72,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ani mladší ako ty by nemal proti mne šancu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:05.12,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.15,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Si to ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.26,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nadišiel čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:16.79,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Znovu budem potrebovať tvoju pomoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:28.08,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Je príliž skoro. Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.02,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo sa zobudil tak skoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:39.02,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, to by si nemala robiť, Aruruu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.06,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Také nadýchané!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:05:00.77,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ponúkla si mi celú svoju existenciu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.99,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja... Ja
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:15.86,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolí ťa niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.64,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Dám ti seba..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:25.33,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Telo aj dušu, dám ti všetko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:37.15,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže, pokiaľ ide o naše plány...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:40.55,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Polovica našich mužov je preč, a z tých, čo sú k dispozícii,\Nlen polovica môže ďalej bojovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:43.86,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď je to len polovica, môžeme ďalej bojovať!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.66,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď budeme len bojovať...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.13,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Bratre...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:54.76,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Bratre!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.90,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa, pokračujme.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:13.82,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si tam vtedy videla?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:17.28,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš, čo sa mi vtedy stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:24.42,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto ti upokojí nervy a uvolníš sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.36,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Eruruu, ty vieš...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:35.41,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prinesiem ti oblečenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.88,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Eruruu, počkaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.15,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:00.67,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:06.24,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Eruruu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.60,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Cítiš sa dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:11.71,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, ja som všetko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:20.82,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, prepáč, ale neprinesla by si mi\N pohár vody?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.12,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.32,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Tá mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.43,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.74,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Zobudili ste sa, Iceman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.34,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mizushima...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:43.04,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako sa cítite?\NSpomínate si na všetko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.01,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, ospravedlňujem sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.58,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:52.21,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by ste si spomenul na niečo o tej maske,\N určite by nám to pomohlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.28,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, pane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:59.32,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimochodom, robí ti číslo 3510 problémy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:03.49,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, neobťažuje ma!\NBola teraz ku mne veľmi milá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:07.57,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, prečo jej hovoríte číslom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:10.94,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Experimentálne objekty nemajú mať meno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.07,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To je pravidlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.07,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Experimentálny objekt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.21,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To je nepríjemné pravidlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:22.75,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak nemáte nič proti tomu, budem ju volať menom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:28.78,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja ju volať menom nebudem,\Nale vy si robte čo chcete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.99,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre, ja musím ísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.59,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Dajte jej pekné meno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:38.99,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Meno, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.20,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké meno by sa ti páčilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:47.17,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Alebo, nepotrebuješ meno?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:54.27,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Profesor mi hovorí Číslo 3510.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:59.12,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja viem... 3, 5, 1, 0...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:03.39,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,San... Go... Mi... Mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.96,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi... Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:06.36,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi... Ko... To...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:07.49,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.12,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.13,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to dobré?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.26,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikoto... Mikoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:19.30,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Som veľmi, veľmi sťastná, Hakuoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.21,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:26.41,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, preber sa, Hakuoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.54,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:38.68,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Eruruu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.46,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto miesto...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:51.60,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa to len deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:04.38,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Starký!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.42,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Len o trochu ďalej...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:17.80,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuya, skry sa tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.10,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Starký...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.28,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám vás!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:45.95,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:49.76,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Avu Kamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.64,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,On zablokoval jeho útok!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:26.13,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten muž... Kto to kčertu je?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:40.60,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to už nejaká chvíľa, Genjimaru, Sakuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:44.44,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Máš pravdu, Hakuoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.61,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vypočujem si váš príbeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:51.61,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunekamun sa vydal cestou záhuby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:12:00.43,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Namiesto spolužitia sa snažia získať\N kontrolu nad ostatnými krajinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:07.07,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,A aj keď spoja všetku krajiny, nepokoje neprestanú,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:09.87,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,a to napokon bude viesť k neodvratnej záhube.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.60,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale predtým, než sa to stane...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:17.61,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcete aby som zhromaždil ľudí a napadol Kunekamun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:22.85,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Správne. Ja, Genjimaru, povediem vás.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:30.06,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To je jediná vec, ktorú môžeme\N urobiť pre Jej Veličenstvo..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:33.47,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, prosím zachráňte ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:38.44,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Stačilo, zdvihni svoju hlavu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:42.74,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Genjimaru, aj keď ste dokázal svoju lojalitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:45.08,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,to čo robíte je stále zakázané.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:50.57,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Verím, že pravá lojalita leží v úpravovaní cesty môjho pána.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.73,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumiem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:12:59.93,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Bratre!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:04.09,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Verím vám. Zverím náš osud do vašich rúk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.53,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Máte moju vďačnosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.21,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že vaše zranenia sú už v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:22.25,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sme sa prvý raz stretli, tiež si sa o mňa takto starala.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:25.71,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To je pravda, bol si zranený po veľkom zemetrasení...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:29.89,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:34.69,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nič! Bolo to vtedy, keď som ťa prvý raz stretla.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:36.82,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:50.50,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Podporila si ma, keď som si myslel, že moje srdce bolo rozbité na kúsky .
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:58.12,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Zostaneš na mojeje strane ako si stála doteraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.45,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:14.50,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Na útok proti Kunekamun,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:19.37,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,musíme získať podporu kmeňov, ktoré sa vzbúrili.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:22.83,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Bude obťiažne veliť toľkým malým kmeňom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:25.74,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolo by to možné, keby bol čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:29.81,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Je tu niekdo, kto to dokáže.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.28,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemyslíš že...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.58,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Genjimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:39.83,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno by sme mohli zachrániť veľkňaza, ktorý\N je držaný na ostrove Saharan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.66,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,a spýtať sa či by nám pomohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.36,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Otec je nažive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:51.30,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, veľkňaz je držaný v žalári na ostrove Saharan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:53.64,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Sestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:56.64,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Bratre!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:40.95,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že už je chladno. Mala by si ísť dovnútra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:41.92,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Poďme...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:46.76,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Eruruu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:47.76,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:50.96,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Eruruu, vyzeráte skľúčená.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.27,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie, len...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.14,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje ruky boli vždy teplé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.30,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale teraz sú studené.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:11.21,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To je asi preto, že sme boli vonku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:21.39,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Hakuoro ti ich zohreje.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:28.79,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože teplo našich rúk pochádza\N od tých, ktorý nás milujú.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:40.15,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Môj brat, Lady Tuskuru, Lord Hakuoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.77,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci mali teplé ruky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:12.90,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžem vstúpiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.41,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Á..Áno!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.48,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeme sa porozprávať?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:32.79,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... o čo by ste sa chceli rozprávať?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:38.94,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to niečo, o čom sa normálne nerozpráva.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:44.47,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým myslíte?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:49.81,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To, čo viedlo náš druh už od počiatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:53.28,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Potom viete, čo robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:58.79,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Som kňazom Onkamiyamukai-ov,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:02.28,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,mojim osudom je pracovať pre Witsalnemitea a ochraňovať ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:05.33,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vedela si to od začiatku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.83,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:12.06,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Najradšej by som bola, keby sa to nikdy nestalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:21.74,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale je tu ešte niečo, čo ti chcem povedať ako žena, nie ako kňaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:31.22,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vaše srdce nepatí nikomu inému, len vám.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:34.95,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mne samej?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.86,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Správne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:42.30,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To je jediná vec, ktorá nemôže byť \Nspútaná ani len dohodou s bohom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:47.07,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto možete stále žiť spôsobom, ktorý chce vaše srdce.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:22.70,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Eruruu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:26.41,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechaj ma takto na chvíľu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:31.54,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem počuť zvuk života,\Nzvuk tlkotu tvojho srdca.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:35.95,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko bude v poriadku,\Npretože počujem ten zvuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:45.10,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, môžeš mi to povedať znovu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:46.27,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:49.20,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To čo si mi povedal včera.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:52.77,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:56.00,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Zostaneš na mojeje strane ako si stála doteraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:58.61,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.30,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Otec!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.50,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Musel som vám robiť starosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:28.63,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vaša Svätosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:32.17,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Som rada, že vás vídim živého.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:42.59,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Je mi potešením stretnúť vás,\NCisára Tuskuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:47.32,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie je potrebné.\NMali sme svoje dôvody, zachrániť vás.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:53.73,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Potrebujete hlas Najvyššieho kňaza, aby ste zjednotili rôzne klany?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:57.20,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, pomôžte nám.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:04.60,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale to už nie je moja starosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.75,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Urutori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:08.04,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:12.71,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Od tohto momentu, ti prenechávam post Najvyššieho Kňaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:16.82,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Sestra...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:18.89,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Urutori...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:21.66,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prímam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:42.21,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst solitude where even flame has frozen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:49.25,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I seek this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:57.80,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Join your soul to mine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:22:06.21,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,And warm me with your love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:14.44,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my words of prayer quiver
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:22.12,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, even if my fragile life is extinguished
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:30.40,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow the flow of the repeating\Ncycles of incarnation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.40,0:22:38.70,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Gazing upon the destiny of an endless world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:46.31,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,You, whose song is sung and sung again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:55.24,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,This evening you doze off, protected...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:23:06.30,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Preložil: Gurthfin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:12.00,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Na ceste záhuby
